  "remarks": "\nA longstanding associate of Alexander Lukashenko, Alexander Shakutin is a leading owner of private enterprise in Belarus. Shakutin has supported the Lukashenko regime despite the fraudulent election result. There are reasonable grounds to suspect that the support of Shakutin for the regime could be contributing to activities undermining democracy.",
